      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few significant dings, and some fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver\u2019s seat, though all major electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that has served us well, priced according to its current state.",
