    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained with obsessive care and stored in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like gloss enhanced by a professional ceramic coating; there are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, with the premium leather upholstery retaining its original matte texture and factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component functions perfectly, and the interior trim is free of any hairline scratches or sun fading. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive binder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance performed at authorized dealerships. It sits on a brand-new set of performance tires and has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection. Included in the sale are all original manuals, two master keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic.",
      "price": 48500.0,
